<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> rājānō nāgavaṁśyāḥ śaśiviśadaya
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śōvyāptadikcakravāḷā jātāstatra babhūva
<lb n="3"/>satguṇanidhi<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīsaṁkyanāmā nṛpaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> jāyā 
<lb n="4"/>tasya tu jāyamēti nṛharē<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>llakṣmīrivāsī
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ttayō<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>jātō gōkamahīpatiḥ paranṛpā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>haṁkārasaṁhārakaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> śākābdē bhujaratna
<lb n="7" break="no"/>bhūśaśimitē sōyaṁ nṛsiṁhātmanō dī
<lb n="8" break="no"/>padvaṁdvakṛtē dhadau varagavāṁ vaṁcōttarāṁ
<lb n="9"/>viṁśatiṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> chāgāṁścāpi viyatśaraissuga
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṇitān śrīdīpadaṁḍadvayaṁ śrīsiṁhādri
<lb n="11" break="no"/>mahāmunīṁdrapuratō gōtrābhivṛddyai
<lb n="12"/>sadā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1192
<lb n="13"/><unclear>nē</unclear>ṁṭi kuṁbha kṛṣṇa daśamiyu śu
<lb n="14" break="no"/>kravāramunāṁḍu śrīmanmahāmaṁ
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ḍalēsvara saṁdyapūṁḍi saṁkyara
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ju koḍuku gōkarājulu tama talli jāya
<lb n="17" break="no"/>madēviki dharmmuvugā vaṁśābhi
<lb n="18" break="no"/>vṛddhigā śrīnarasiṁhyanāthuniki
<lb n="19"/>Akaṁḍadīpamu reṁṭikiṁgāṁ be
<lb n="20" break="no"/>ṭu mōdālu Īruvaḍēnu goṟi
<lb n="21" break="no"/>yalu Ēṁbhai Ī dharmmuvu śrīvaiṣṇa
<lb n="22" break="no"/>va rakṣa <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

